 INFO
------------------------------------------------------------

Tools created to help streamline tasks within the Flash IDE.
Info about each command: http://blog.tomorrowevening.com/tag/jsfl/


 INSTALL
------------------------------------------------------------

- Replace "[Version]" with whatever Flash version you're using
- Extract files to designated areas
- Restart Flash IDE


* Windows Vista™:
boot drive\Users\username\Local Settings\Application Data\Adobe\Flash [Version]\language\Configuration\

* Windows® XP:
boot drive\Documents and Settings\username\Local Settings\Application Data\Adobe\Flash [Version]\language\Configuration\

* Mac OS® X:
Macintosh HD/Users/username/Library/Application Support/Adobe/Flash [Version]/language/Configuration/


More info about JSFL here: http://help.adobe.com/en_US/Flash/10.0_ExtendingFlash/WS5b3ccc516d4fbf351e63e3d118a9024f3f-7fe8.html



